‚ñ° Error #6: [Specific concept/misconception]
‚ñ° Error #7: [Specific concept/misconception]
‚ñ° Error #8: [Specific concept/misconception]

CONCLUSION SECTION:
‚ñ° Error #9: [Specific concept/misconception]
‚ñ° Error #10: [Specific concept/misconception]
```

### AGE-SPECIFIC ERROR TYPES
**Select appropriate error types for your age group:**

- **Ages 4-7**: Process misconceptions, simple fact reversals
- **Ages 8-11**: Logical reasoning errors, cause-effect confusion
- **Ages 12-14**: Evidence evaluation errors, source credibility mistakes
- **Ages 15-17**: Research literacy errors, methodology misconceptions
- **Ages 18+**: Professional competency errors, expert-level misconceptions

